plot: Timmy Can't Find a Date to Dimmsdale's Elementry School Friday the 13th Dance. So he then remembers Cindy (From the First Jimmy Timmy Power Hour) and Then Goes to Retroville but takes Cosmo and Wanda with him. But Jimmy was planning on asking Cindy to the Linnberg Elementry School Dance. Jimmy and Timmy then preform Magic vs Science which then attracts Professior Calamorious Jimmy Neutron's arch enemy. But the Anti Fairies then escape from their prison and Anti Cosmo meets Calamorious and betrays him later. Can Jimmy and Timmy Save Then?
title: The Jimmy Timmy Power Hour 2: When Nerds Collide
